{"tid":1077781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國反一帶一路 警告義：將嘗苦果","createTime":"2019-03-25T23:22:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T05:58:09.000Z","uid":141151,"like":54,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"32a26b1021c6bfc35e0e392239cfe14f010ba321","tid":1077781,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T23:22:26.000Z","msg":"德國反一帶一路 警告義：將嘗苦果<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/20190326/38291770/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2F20190326%2F38291770%2F&d=Fb7z1ilWoLc7MobAJ3fbq0YnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=2752dcdc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2F20190326%2F38291770%2F&h=8653f237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/20190326/38291770/</a><br />\n<br />\n義大利加入中國的「一帶一路」計劃，成為七大工業國（G7）第一個擁抱一帶一路的成員國，引發歐洲國家批評，德國外交部長馬斯（Heiko Maas）前天警告，中國並非自由的民主國家，「只顧眼前的利益，會比原來預料還早嘗到苦果」，一些國家如果以為，與中國做生意能得到比較多好處，會驚訝根本不是這麼一回事，且醒來時才發現自己依賴中國。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>義記者遭陸官員威脅</strong><br />\n馬斯強調，中國毫不留情在全世界捍衛自身利益，歐盟國家唯有聯合起來，才能克服中國與俄羅斯等「巨人」帶來的挑戰。北京透過一帶一路的基礎建設投資，擴大對歐洲的影響力，歐盟成員對歐洲可能因此被分化多次表示憂心，德國總理梅克爾（Angela Merkel）上周在歐盟高峰會上，沒有直接批評義大利加入一帶一路，但強調「歐洲聯合行動會更好」。 <br />\n<br />\n此外，義大利《羅馬日報》報導，中國國家主席習近平日前訪問義大利期間，該報女記者龐皮利（Giulia Pompili）竟遭中國大使館官員楊涵（音譯，Yang Han）威脅，多次要她「停止說中國的壞話」，甚至還要拿走她的手機。該報在一帶一路的議題上與羅馬官方立場相左，對此事表示「義大利不是中國，羅馬也不是北京。」無國界記者組織東亞地區負責人艾偉昂（Cedric Alviani）指出，中國外交官員類似鴨霸言行越來越普遍，民主國家必須對此作出回應，媒體與政界都不應接受類似壓力。國際中心"},{"pid":"d568a61a1a7734492026f45b30cb86a45adf9996","tid":1077781,"uid":10637,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T23:24:44.000Z","msg":"德國係咁彈出彈入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce8a59312eca34750f2f98a333b67419549d5cd","tid":1077781,"uid":550,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T23:24:54.000Z","msg":"意大利幾時都係累全家<br />\n德國心諗：人類......"},{"pid":"2a6ef06214b5ee32267380f97e2931cb11d8419e","tid":1077781,"uid":550,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"d568a61a1a7734492026f45b30cb86a45adf9996","tid":1077781,"uid":10637,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T23:24:44.000Z","msg":"德國係咁彈出彈入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T23:26:16.000Z","msg":"反一帶一路但唔反華為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係話新華社有獨立自主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0cb91c46d3dd8443248a27bfca19ad5bbb80bd","tid":1077781,"uid":5601,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T23:26:27.000Z","msg":"德國自己都同屎為合作啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3fe8137e8718330158137ba48eb8fbf8e14257","tid":1077781,"uid":105795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T23:33:11.000Z","msg":"德國比美國佬出聲屌完就即刻轉駄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38554488b8bde492df1d623487ed9cd123a6884","tid":1077781,"uid":13592,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:08:45.000Z","msg":"我成日以為 歐盟成員國係唔可以自己去簽協議"},{"pid":"e08b537d135a9bcd6c55662d4fb666a6955f0075","tid":1077781,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:10:22.000Z","msg":"有個bug位<br />\n<br />\n又話歐盟國家唔可以同外國直接傾trade deal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd763c71bc0a3c9cd3b6b662d43ad38f508eb65","tid":1077781,"uid":29080,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:20:16.000Z","msg":"德：又係你條仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa969dd7d04b6c88dc7ff90ca82eb64243b250b","tid":1077781,"uid":35814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:22:46.000Z","msg":"我好亂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class